adjectives.description: quietlike (comparative more quietlike, superlative most quietlike)

entries.meaning: Indicative or characteristic of quietness or of being quiet.
examples: Me, no, wouldn't hurt nobody, but where the fuck was I? Guess I wasn't so much in school, this serene quietlike country setting, as sitting on the spare tire of an open gun jeep manning an M-60 machine gun, patrolling a mountain side, [...]

adverbs.description: quietlike (comparative more quietlike, superlative most quietlike)

examples: "[...] I can watch her quietlike... like a man."
